text: == Events == * Outbreak of the First Sino-Japanese War * June 30 – Tower Bridge in London opened. == Births == * February 10 - Harold Macmillan, British Prime Minister * April 17 – Nikita Krushchev, Soviet leader * March 20 – Ky Ebright, American Olympic rowing coach (d. 1979) * July 26 – Aldous Huxley, English writer * November 27 - Katherine Milhous, American illustrator and writer (d. 1977) == Deaths == * 1 January – Heinrich Rudolf Hertz * 1 November - Alexander III of Russia Czar of Russia father of Czar Nicholas II
